import React from 'react'

const SideBarToggle = ({handleSidebarToggle, sidebarOpen}) => {

    return (

    <>
    <svg
        onClick={handleSidebarToggle}
        className="fixed top-0 h-9 w-9 z-20 sm:hidden block border border-[#424549] rounded-md ml-1 mt-4"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke="#8398e6"
    >
        <path
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
        strokeWidth="2"
        d={` ${
        !sidebarOpen 
        ? 'M4 6h16M4 12h16m-7 6h7' // draws 3 horizontal line icon
        : 'M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12'}`} // draws X icon
        />    
    </svg>
    </>
    )
}

export default SideBarToggle
